milestones.description: Dave Houghton has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Iain Butchart's 2
Jarvis and Andy Pycroft's 36-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 27 between John Traicos and Vince Hogg
This is the lowest match aggregate (271) involving teams India & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
